778
01:14:59,242 --> 01:15:00,834
...and the insect is awake.

779
01:15:02,322 --> 01:15:03,835
No, Seth.

780
01:15:05,482 --> 01:15:07,234
I'm saying...

781
01:15:09,802 --> 01:15:12,032
...I'll hurt you if you stay.

782
01:15:33,602 --> 01:15:36,560
(GROANS)

783
01:15:49,842 --> 01:15:51,719
Let's go. Let's do it now.

784
01:15:51,922 --> 01:15:54,834
Now? Wait.
Wait a minute. What did he say?

785
01:15:55,442 --> 01:15:58,036
I couldn't tell him.
Let's go, damn it.

786
01:15:58,242 --> 01:16:00,756
No! I think we should
wait a few days.

787
01:16:01,002 --> 01:16:02,515
You're not
in the right state of mind.

788
01:16:03,082 --> 01:16:05,915
I want it out of my body now.
You should have seen him.

789
01:16:06,122 --> 01:16:08,477
There could be anything in here,
in me, in my body.

790
01:16:08,722 --> 01:16:11,634
I don't know if I can
arrange it now, tonight.

791
01:16:11,842 --> 01:16:13,036
Why do we have to...?

792
01:16:13,242 --> 01:16:18,157
I don't want it. Understand?
I don't want it in my body!

793
01:16:50,722 --> 01:16:53,441
Well, okay, what's the story?

794
01:16:56,122 --> 01:16:58,238
She's pregnant
and she wants an abortion.

795
01:16:58,802 --> 01:17:00,155
In the middle of the night?

796
01:17:02,242 --> 01:17:04,437
We have good reason to think that...

797
01:17:04,642 --> 01:17:08,032
...this child will be deformed.

798
01:17:08,442 --> 01:17:11,240
- Yeah, but in the middle of the night?
- Look, Brent.

799
01:17:13,242 --> 01:17:14,311
Please.

800
01:17:16,522 --> 01:17:17,557
Is it your child?

801
01:17:18,522 --> 01:17:19,432
No.

802
01:17:22,682 --> 01:17:26,800
It's the child of a man
who is deformed.

803
01:17:28,482 --> 01:17:29,881
I don't mean to interfere...

804
01:17:30,082 --> 01:17:33,836
...but I detect a certain
uncertainty here.

805
01:17:34,082 --> 01:17:36,835
There are tests we can do
to determine whether...

806
01:17:37,082 --> 01:17:41,041
I don't want tests.
Tests can't guarantee anything.

807
01:17:41,402 --> 01:17:44,439
The baby could start off normal,
then become...

808
01:17:47,442 --> 01:17:48,841
I want an abortion.

809
01:17:51,722 --> 01:17:53,838
I'll do it myself if I have to.

810
01:17:54,922 --> 01:17:58,631
If you'll slip into that,
we'll be on our way in no time.

811
01:18:24,442 --> 01:18:25,431
No.

812
01:18:28,922 --> 01:18:30,799
Wait, Seth, no.

813
01:18:55,402 --> 01:18:57,632
Why did you want to kill Brundle?

814
01:18:58,802 --> 01:19:03,637
The baby might be all that's left
of the real me.

815
01:19:06,322 --> 01:19:07,675
Please don't kill me.

816
01:19:09,282 --> 01:19:12,399
I can't have it. I'm afraid.

817
01:19:12,722 --> 01:19:16,271
Please, have the baby.

818
01:19:17,002 --> 01:19:17,991
I can't.

819
01:19:18,522 --> 01:19:20,240
I can't.

820
01:19:22,122 --> 01:19:23,635
Too bad.

821
01:19:28,322 --> 01:19:29,835
Too bad.

822
01:21:40,722 --> 01:21:41,598
(SCREECHES)

823
01:21:45,802 --> 01:21:47,235
Jesus!

824
01:21:50,602 --> 01:21:51,591
Ah!

825
01:22:53,242 --> 01:22:56,439
VERONICA:
No, don't. Don't, please.

826
01:22:56,802 --> 01:22:58,030
Please.

827
01:23:20,042 --> 01:23:21,236
Help me.

828
01:23:22,042 --> 01:23:23,031
Help me be human.

829
01:23:24,802 --> 01:23:26,030
How?

830
01:23:33,522 --> 01:23:34,841
Well...

831
01:23:38,082 --> 01:23:39,640
I go there...

832
01:23:42,082 --> 01:23:43,515
...and you go there.

833
01:23:47,842 --> 01:23:50,436
We come apart...

834
01:23:50,802 --> 01:23:55,159
...and then we come together there.

835
01:23:57,722 --> 01:24:00,361
You, me and the baby.

836
01:24:01,642 --> 01:24:02,631
Together.

837
01:24:19,322 --> 01:24:20,311
No...

838
01:24:21,322 --> 01:24:23,438
We'll be the ultimate family.

839
01:24:23,922 --> 01:24:28,120
A family of three,
joined together in one body.

840
01:24:29,442 --> 01:24:31,433
More human than I am alone.

841
01:24:32,842 --> 01:24:35,037
No, no!

842
01:24:42,682 --> 01:24:44,035
(CHOKES)

843
01:24:56,202 --> 01:24:58,352
Oh, God. Please!

844
01:25:10,402 --> 01:25:13,041
Oh, God, please!

845
01:26:56,242 --> 01:26:57,721
(VERONICA GASPING)

846
01:27:36,242 --> 01:27:37,357
(SCREAMS)

847
01:28:40,802 --> 01:28:42,838
No, I can't.

848
01:28:44,722 --> 01:28:46,235
I can't.

849
01:28:50,522 --> 01:28:52,433
No. Oh, God!

